ED_Title: Programme planning  (Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee))
ED_DecisionText:
At its 45th plenary meeting, on 7 December 2023, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Special
Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee).  (Footnote: A/78/431.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
